{
  "title": "Deliciously Dense Southern Thai Millet Pilaf",
  "description": "A fatty and bouncy Southern Thai dish featuring millet, namul-blanch-season, and vegetarian-friendly ingredients, this pilaf is perfect for adventurous eaters. It combines the richness of coconut milk with the spiciness of Thai chilies.",
  "cuisine": "Southern Thai",
